Operationala costs: 
Cloud computing can help finances by: 
-> Providing cost-effective subsction
-> Reduce infrastructure and upgrade costs
-> Enabling faster releases with automatic upgrades.
-> Improving usability  of services including reporting, analytics and predictive analysis using AI and MI servies in cloud.
-> Opportunities for process improvement and agility,faster reporting and shorter planning cycles.
-> Enabling growth 
-> Supporitng business transformation upgrading finance systems and processes with the latest available on demand resources in the cloud.
